&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use Scikit-learn to track an example ML project end to end 
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explore several models, including support vector machines, decision trees, random forests, and ensemble methods 
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Exploit unsupervised learning techniques such as dimensionality reduction, clustering, and anomaly detection 
