&lt;i&gt;Build a Large Language Model (from Scratch)&lt;/i&gt; teaches you how to:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Plan and code all the parts of an LLM&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Prepare a dataset suitable for LLM training&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fine-tune LLMs for text classification and with your own data&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use human feedback to ensure your LLM follows instructions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Load pretrained weights into an LLM&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
